{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-special-spelling-rules/task-6","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor punih slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-special-spelling-rules","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U Pinyinu, slogovi 16 se smatraju kompletnim jedinicama umesto da se dele na početne konsonante i krajnje vokale. Ovo se zove <strong>kompletan slog</strong>.</p>\n<p>Ovo su <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">chi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ri</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ci</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">si</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wu</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yu</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ye</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yue</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yuan</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yin</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yun</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ying</span>. Već ste videli neke od njih u prethodnim lekcijama.</p>\n<p>Ovde ćete naučiti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">chi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ri</span>. U ovim silabama, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span> ne predstavlja uobičajeni vokalni zvuk. Umesto toga, on/ona predstavlja jedinstveni zvučni dodatak povezan sa konsonantima <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zh</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ch</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">sh</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">r</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite potpune slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shi</span> u različitim tonomima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shī</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">师</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shí</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">十</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shǐ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">史</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shì</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">是</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-special-spelling-rules/task-6"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company1-breakroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Chen Na","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_special_spelling_rules.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":77.32,"finishTimestamp":93.31},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Chen Na","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Chen Na","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.95,"dialogue":{"text":"zhi","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Chen Na","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":2.7,"finishTime":3.91,"dialogue":{"text":"chi","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Chen Na","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":4.75,"finishTime":5.93,"dialogue":{"text":"shi","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Chen Na","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":6.93,"finishTime":7.96,"dialogue":{"text":"ri","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Chen Na","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":9.97,"finishTime":11.1,"dialogue":{"tex